export const staticExample =  "casetype: "static"
variables: {time, detection, lane}
values: {{"day", "twilight", "night"}, {"detected", "not detected"}, {"out", "in"}}
numsamples: 100

independence
condindep[{time, lane}, {detection}]

main
P[detection = "detected" | time = "day"] = .75
P[detection = "detected" | time = "twilight"] = .4
P[detection = "detected" | time = "night"] = .2
P[time = "day"] = .6
P[time = "twilight"] = P[time = "night"]
P[lane = "out"] = .2
P[detection = "detected" | lane = "in"] = .6";

export const timeInvariantExample = "casetype: "timeinvariant"
variables: {latency, ping}
values: {{"low", "high"}, {"low", "high"}}
timesteps: {0, 1}
numsamples: 100

independence
condindep[{latency[t], ping[t-1]}, {ping[t]}]

main
P[ping[t] = "high" | ping[t-1] = "high"] = .7
P[ping[t] = "low" | ping[t-1] = "low"] = .65
P[latency[t] = "low"] = .8
P[ping[t] = "high" | latency[t] = "high"] = .6";

export const timeVariantExample = "casetype: "timevariant"
variables: {tool, operation}
values: {{"broken", "func"}, {"fail", "ok"}}
timesteps: {1, 0}
numsamples: 100

independence
indep[{operation[t], tool[t-1]}]

basecase
P[tool[0] = "func"] = .9

main
P[tool[t] = "broken" | tool[t-1] = "broken"] = 1
P[operation[t] = "ok"] = .8
P[tool[t] = "func"] = .9*P[tool[t-1] = "func"]
P[operation[t] = "ok" && tool[t] = "func"] = .95*P[operation[t] = "ok" && tool[t-1] = "func"]";
